<td width="15"><img src="/forums/images/warninglevel.gif" width="16" height="16" Alt="Numo's Warning Level: 0"></td><td align="left" nowrap><font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Level: 0 </font></td>
